OL,3,CTrain driver minimum age to be lowered
OL,4,Cto 18 from June
OL,6,F"This change will open doors for those
OL,7,Fwanting to move straight into the
OL,8,Fworkplace, giving a younger generation
OL,9,Fthe chance to build rewarding careers
OL,10,Fin the railway, whether that's in
OL,11,Ffreight or passenger services.
OL,13,F"It's a move that will help secure the
OL,14,Ffuture of Great British Railways and
OL,15,Fthe wider rail industry, and ensure
OL,16,Fthe workforce reflects the energy,
OL,17,Ftalent and ambition of the next
OL,18,Fgeneration."
