OL,3,CTrain driver minimum age to be lowered
OL,4,Cto 18 from June
OL,6,FSwitzerland, Germany and Australia
OL,7,Falready allow 18-year-olds to operate
OL,8,Ftrains.
OL,10,FIt is planned to "level the playing
OL,11,Ffield across the transport sector", as
OL,12,F18-year-olds can already drive a Tube
OL,13,Ftrain or tram on the Transport for
OL,14,FLondon network, or become a pilot.
OL,16,FWork and Pensions Secretary Pat
OL,17,FMcFadden said: "With almost a million
OL,18,Fyoung people not in education,
OL,19,Femployment or training, we need to
OL,20,Fopen up new routes into skilled, well-
OL,21,Fpaid careers.
