OL,3,CTrain driver minimum age to be lowered
OL,4,Cto 18 from June
OL,6,F"Lowering the minimum age for train
OL,7,Fdrivers puts young people at the
OL,8,Fcontrols ` of a train today, and of
OL,9,Ftheir own futures tomorrow."
OL,11,FDave Calfe, general secretary of train
OL,12,Fdrivers' union, Aslef, said the
OL,13,Fdecision will "increase diversity in
OL,14,Fthe driver's cab by encouraging more
OL,15,Fyoung people from all communities to
OL,16,Fdrive trains".
OL,18,FHe added: "At the moment, many young
OL,19,Fpeople make their career choice at 18
OL,20,Fand the industry misses out as the
OL,21,Fcurrent minimum age is 20.
